 1 分，莫尔加德请求暂停。回到场上樊振东又追 1 分扳平，相持中莫尔加德反手失误，樊振东以 8 比 7 反超。之后樊振东乘胜追击又拿 2 分，他以 10 比 7 拿到赛点。莫尔加德挽救一个赛点，下一球他接发球抢攻，樊振东把球挡回得分，11 比 8，樊振东赢下第四局以 4 比 0 获胜夺冠。樊振东 4 比 0 横扫瑞典黑马 首次问鼎世乒赛男单冠军"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-d7bf04de9e4e50f63b07237e083cebd6_b.jpeg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "56 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/502606287"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IyIf+sua57YVCEAMaCDczOTcxMzc2IOiSlo0GMAM4qwFALXIJNTAyNjA2Mjg3eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "46_1638252469.2810674", "card_id": "Q_501515073", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 111}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "当孩子问「为什么讨好别人叫做『拍马屁』而不是『拍牛屁』『拍羊屁』」如何回答？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-9303fccd490978abcd1f25a58ce750e3_1440w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "53 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/501515073"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IyIf+sua57YVCEAMaCDczNzI4OTU1ILrj/IwGMBw46QJALnIJNTAxNTE1MDczeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "47_1638252469.281529", "card_id": "Q_26992286", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 127}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "为什么要给马钉马掌？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-cf925eb348805357f4bff9ce1e05e58b_720w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "52 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/26992286"}}, "attached_info": "Cj0IyIf+sua57YVCEAMaBzI5Nzk4OTEg+4eapAUwCDihFUAvcggyNjk5MjI4NngAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "48_1638252469.2819996", "card_id": "Q_502418129", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 30